Package plt.dataset.preprocessing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Binary
    Transforms a nominal feature into a set of binary features, one for each different value
    FeaturePreprocessingInfo
    Preprocessing options selected for an input feature
    Ignoring
    Placeholder preprocessing operation used with features that are selected to not be included in the model
    MinMax
    Transforms the values of a feature to have the new minimum and maximum values specified
    Nominal
    Cast the values of a feature as nominal
    Numeric
    Cast the values of a feature as a numeric
    NumericBinary
    Transforms a numeric feature into a set of binary features, one for each different value
    PreprocessingOperation  
    PreprocessingSelector
    Preprocessing operation selected for an input feature
    ZScore
    Transforms the values of a feature to have average equal to zero and standard deviation equal to one
